蕾哈娜 (Rihanna) 词曲作者揭示了近 20 年来不为人知的《SOS》诗句中的模式https://www.nme.com/news/music/rihanna-songwriter-reveals-pattern-in-sos-verse-thats-gone-unknown-for-nearly-20-years-3803549?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=蕾哈娜歌曲作者揭示了近 20 年来不为人知的求救诗句模式Surej SinghThu, 17 Oct 2024 01:45:10 +0000 Music NewsNewsPopR&B https://www.nme.com/?p=3803549 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/rihanna@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/rihanna@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/rihanna@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/rihanna@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/rihanna@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/rihanna@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/rihanna@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “这首歌的整个第二节都是 80 年代的歌曲标题串成句子”</p><p>这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rihanna-songwriter-reveals-pattern-in-sos-verse-thats-gone-unknown-for-nearly-20-years-3803549">后蕾哈娜 (Rihanna) 作曲家揭示了《SOS》诗句中的模式，该诗句在近 20 年来一直不为人知，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/rihanna@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/rihanna@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/rihanna@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/rihanna@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/rihanna@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/rihanna@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/rihanna@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rihanna">蕾哈娜</a>(Rihanna) 的《SOS》的词曲作者透露了这首歌近二十年来不为人知的模式 - 看看下面的模式。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/rihanna-every-album-ranked-and-rated-2921163">蕾哈娜：每张专辑的排名和评级</a></strong></li></ul><p>在最近接受<em>Behind the Wall</em>采访时，歌曲作者 Evan &#39;Kidd&#39; Bogart（他与 Edward Cobb 和 Jonathan Rotem 共同创作了这首歌的歌词）透露了有关这首 2006 年热门歌曲的新信息。鲍嘉创作了这首歌的整个第二节，他现在透露这是对 20 世纪 80 年代歌曲标题的致敬。</p><p>鲍嘉说：“当我写这本书时，我不知道自己在做什么。那首歌的整个第二节都是 80 年代的歌曲标题串成句子，因为我认为这很聪明……它们都是 80 年代的第一首歌。”</p><p>他接着剖析了这首诗的一部分，其中包括提到<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/a-ha">A-Ha</a>的“Take On Me”、Cutting Crew 的“(I Just) Died in Your Arms Tonight”、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tears-for-fears">Tears For Fears 的</a>“Head Over Heels”、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kim-wilde">金·王尔德</a>的《You Keep Me Hangin&#39; On》和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michael-jackson">迈克尔·杰克逊</a>的《The Way You Make Me Feel》。 </p><blockquote class="tiktok-embed" cite="https://www.tiktok.com/@danielswall/video/7426227251647171882" data-video-id="7426227251647171882" data-embed-from="oembed" style="max-width:605px; min-width:325px;"><section> <a target="_blank" title="@丹尼尔斯沃尔" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@danielswall?refer=embed">@丹尼尔斯沃尔</a></p><p>回复 @NANZ 为什么蕾哈娜的第一首<a title="1" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/1?refer=embed">排名第一的</a>歌曲有一个秘密 在我们与埃文·“基德”·博加特的对话中，他揭示了他多年前为蕾哈娜写的最伟大歌曲之一背后的令人惊讶的秘密——一个从未有人注意到的细节。这是我们完整对话的片段@kiddbogart @Rihanna <a title="歌手" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/singer?refer=embed">#singer</a> <a title="作曲家" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/songwriter?refer=embed">#songwriter</a> <a title="蕾哈娜" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/rihanna?refer=embed">#rihanna</a> <a title="求救" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/sos?refer=embed">#sos<